        "subject": "LU-9943 lnet: fix WR accounting for the FastReg mode",
        "message": "LU-9943 lnet: fix WR accounting for the FastReg mode\n\nFastReg memory model need a two additional WR's per transfer.\nFirst one for memory window registration, second one for the\nmemory window invalidate.\n\nLack accounting for these WR's may caused a bug\n    mlx5_warn:mlx5_0:begin_wqe:4085:(pid 9590): work queue overflow\n\n\nSigned-off-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey.lyashkov@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: I7479b5de5119a4b6ba5847718094c592f6a87056\n"
